name: CBE Exam Seat Quota
query:
select 
cbe_exam_date as "Exam Date:Data:100",
shift as "Shift:Data:250",
23 as "Total Seats:Int:150",
count(name) as "Occupied Seats:Int:150",
23 - count(name) as"Available Seats:Int:150"
from `tabCBE Registration`
where docstatus = 1 and status = "Paid"

group by cbe_exam_date, shift
order by cast(concat(right(cbe_exam_date, 4), "-", right(left(REPLACE(cbe_exam_date, '-', ''), 4), 2), "-", left(cbe_exam_date, 2)) as datetime), shift
